{"id":261368,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/bbc-中国报摘：十八大报告咨询/","date":"2012-11-06T07:15:23Z","modified":"2012-11-06T07:15:23Z","title":"BBC | 中国报摘：十八大报告咨询","content":"<div>\n<div><img width=\"304\" height=\"171\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2012/11/06/121106044956_cn_tiananmen_police_304x171_ap.jpg\" alt=\"北京天安门广场一大型电子显示屏前两名武警在巡逻（5/11/2012）\" /></p>\n<p>北京在十八大临近之际不断加强安保。</p>\n</div>\n<p>星期二（11月6日）的中国报章报道，中共就提交十八大的工作报告召开了党外人士座谈会。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpc.people.com.cn%2F18%2Fn%2F2012%2F1106%2Fc350821-19507106.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《人民日报》</span></a>与 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fcndy%2F2012-11%2F06%2Fcontent_15877882.htm\"><span>按键</span> <span>英文《中国日报》</span></a>等报道，国家主席胡锦涛出席了会议，“听取各民主党派中央、全国工商联领导人和无党派人士的意见和建议”。</p>\n<p>中国除中共外尚有八个“ <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Ftest%2F2008-04%2F03%2Fcontent_935826.htm\"><span>按键</span> <span>民主党派</span></a>”，这些政党服从于中共领导的“多党合作制度”，角色与其他国家的在野党不同。</p>\n<p>报道称，与会代表认为中共中央“全方位推进改革开放”，使中国的“经济建设、政治建设、文化建设、社会建设以及生态文明建设取得显著成就，民生持续改善”。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F20121106%2Fcaa3.htm\"><span>按键</span> <span>香港《明报》</span></a>指出，这次座谈会早于9月3日举行，但官方新华社直到星期一（5日）才报道这消息。</p>\n<p>报道说，笃定接任国家主席和总理职务的国家副主席习近平和副总理李克强均出席了该次座谈会。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.com%2Fyesterday%2Fchi%2F1106eo01.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>香港《星岛日报》</span></a>则报道，新华社星期一刊发长篇评论，重申了中共在政治改革上不会“误入歧途”，走西方多党民主制度的道路。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fepaper.jinghua.cn%2Fhtml%2F2012-11%2F06%2Fcontent_1790638.htm\"><span>按键</span> <span>《京华时报》</span></a>与 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fgcontent.oeeee.com%2Ff%2Ffc%2Fffc7ad29e9362b82%2FBlog%2F8f1%2F56ba51.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>广州《南方都市报》</span></a>等地方报章报道了各地党代表抵达北京的消息。《环球时报》英文版头版报道，超过1000名外国记者报名采访中共十八大会议，比2007年的十七大“显著增加”。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpc.people.com.cn%2Fn%2F2012%2F1106%2Fc64094-19507105.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《人民日报》</span></a>与 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fepaper.jinghua.cn%2Fhtml%2F2012-11%2F06%2Fcontent_1790627.htm\"><span>按键</span> <span>《京华时报》</span></a>还报道，中共政法委书记周永康在巡视北京安保工作时强调，“要坚决防止危险人员、危险物品、危险车辆进入北京，确保首都安全稳定”。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.com%2Fyesterday%2Fchi%2F1106eo02.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《星岛日报》</span></a>报道，北京丰台区城管人员要求区内居民“自觉‘禁飞’”风筝和孔明灯。</p>\n<p>另一方面， <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F20121106%2Fcaa1.htm\"><span>按键</span> <span>《明报》</span></a>报道，不少网民在三大官方喉舌网站——新华网、人民网和央视网——留言要求加大反贪腐力度。在严密的审查制度下，分析认为当局有意公开这些意见。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fopinion%2F2012-11%2F06%2Fcontent_15877958.htm\"><span>按键</span> <span>《中国日报》社评</span></a>称，中共自十七大以来惩处了66万名违反党纪干部，证明了中共反腐败的决心。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fopinion.huanqiu.com%2Feditorial%2F2012-11%2F3246879.html\"><span>按键</span> <span>《环球时报》双语社评</span></a>则针对更大范围的社会矛盾评论说：“官方和民间都首先需要了解政府能力实际在下降的事实。官方要清楚自己能决定一切的想法已不合时宜，不受监督做事的环境更不可能重现。”</p>\n<p>“官方需要有更多依靠民间力量解决问题的战略思考和政策安排，逐步实现大政府和大社会的平衡统一。”</p>\n<p>不过香港英文《南华早报》说，中国老百姓似乎仍处于“一面倒的意识冷淡”当中，不少人认为十八大“与自己无关”。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dFc0V1d0REQ4RkJ5d25uWFowVTNhWUE6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"328\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代 </a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":998,"categories":[18270,18269,8779],"tags":[9098,19189]}